                <fr:title text="The matrix associated to a finite relation">The <fr:link href="/jms-00IS/" title="Matrix over a semiring" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00IS/" display-uri="jms-00IS" type="local">matrix</fr:link> associated to a finite <fr:link href="/jms-00I7/" title="Relation" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00I7/" display-uri="jms-00I7" type="local">relation</fr:link></fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[R\colon {\mathopen {}\left  [m\right  ]\mathclose {}}\mathbin {\nrightarrow }{\mathopen {}\left  [n\right  ]\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> be a <fr:link href="/jms-00I7/" title="Relation" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00I7/" display-uri="jms-00I7" type="local">relation</fr:link>; for any semiring <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[S]]></fr:tex>, we may form the <html:em><html:strong><html:span style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[{\mathopen {}\left (n\times  n\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>-<fr:link href="/jms-00I7/" title="Relation" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00I7/" display-uri="jms-00I7" type="local">matrix</fr:link></html:span> over <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[S]]></fr:tex> associated to <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[R]]></fr:tex></html:strong></html:em> as follows:</html:p>
                <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[
 {\mathopen {}\left (\operatorname {\underline {mat}}_S{R}\right )\mathclose {}}_{i\in {\mathopen {}\left  [m\right  ]\mathclose {}},j\in {\mathopen {}\left  [n\right  ]\mathclose {}}} =
 \begin {cases}
   1&\text {if } i\mathrel {R}j
   \\
   0&\text {otherwise}
 \end {cases}
]]></fr:tex>
                <html:p>We have defined a function <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {\underline {mat}}_S\colon  \mathrm {Rel}{\mathopen {}\left ({\mathopen {}\left  [m\right  ]\mathclose {}},{\mathopen {}\left  [n\right  ]\mathclose {}}\right )\mathclose {}} \to  \mathrm {Mat}_{S}{\mathopen {}\left (m,n\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
              </fr:mainmatter>
